name: Nebit
Lore: 'Jawa leader responsible for organizing raids on rival Jawa factions. Detested warrior. Hates being ''frocked.''',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. When in a battle with at least two of your other Jawas, adds one battle destiny. When your total battle destiny at Nebit''s site is greater than opponent''s total battle destiny, Nebit reduces attrition against you by 3.',
